What is the purpose of running PhotonVision on a Windows laptop?
A laptop is not a good vision platform for robots imo - heavy, bulky, fragile, etc.
The only reason we ship Windows binaries is to ease testing and development, not with the intent they end up on a robot.

As to this error, I’m unsure, but I’d suggest not spending any time on it given the above.
